      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Eligible Liverpool households on qualifying benefits can receive a free boiler or central heating installation through the ECO4 scheme. Here is who qualifies, what is covered and how to apply before funding runs out.</p>
      <div class="blog-meta">
